    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名在逃的太空难民。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 邪恶的太空皇帝已经宣布了所有的“界地巫侍”都必须被处死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 而你唯一的武器……是一把可以弹开激光弹的侍刀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你的任务：<strong>死地求生</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>玩法特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/b1d02ba334cdf1fdde5f9e09443dabd2.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/b1d02ba334cdf1fdde5f9e09443dabd2.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/048e93ea8ab56577f547f0ddbbfa2587.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 弹开敌人的激光弹，使其调转方向，让他们搬石砸脚！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/4ff3340e6e7e5cdebc9a9abd1d01a6c0.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/4ff3340e6e7e5cdebc9a9abd1d01a6c0.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/b2d46e33daa2eda5e28be6c9431bdf70.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/b2d46e33daa2eda5e28be6c9431bdf70.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/b2d46e33daa2eda5e28be6c9431bdf70.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 学习并掌握各种派系，最终达成配合，融会贯通。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/88ec2b0f26d465473db855afa54ab746.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/88ec2b0f26d465473db855afa54ab746.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/f7f3723853f2068fa1532a89b2dee072.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/f7f3723853f2068fa1532a89b2dee072.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 即便你孤身一人，“巫魔界气”的力量将一直陪伴着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/91d5023991b4c6079c69c286a25d352d.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/91d5023991b4c6079c69c286a25d352d.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a57d154140677b28cb58586540102864.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80 年代首屈一指的美术风格，重现界地巫侍的经典。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/bc46c32f967321ffe0544032c8b91076.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/bc46c32f967321ffe0544032c8b91076.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.poster.avif?t=1741927316\" width=618 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.webm?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116810/extras/a2ee78bba7822c8a7321938504571e62.mp4?t=1741927316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 酣畅玩法，每局不超过 15 分钟，让你的快乐无以复加。</p>",
